A cyberpunk-style digital illustration depicting streams of glowing data particles flowing through interconnected translucent pipes and channels in a dark urban environment. Multiple luminescent orbs of varying colors (cyan, magenta, orange) represent different data types, traveling through a complex network of crystalline tubes that branch, merge, and filter through geometric gateway structures. The scene shows these particles being transformed as they pass through hexagonal filter nodes that glow with neon purple light. In the background, towering dark monolithic server structures loom with subtle circuit patterns etched into their surfaces. The overall atmosphere is moody with deep blacks and electric blues, with the flowing particle streams creating dynamic light trails that illuminate the scene. Rain-slicked surfaces reflect the neon glow of the data streams, adding depth and atmosphere to this visualization of reactive data flowing through observable pipelines.
